<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Shape C covers the most space. Shape A can be made with 7 triangles. Shape B can be made with 8 triangles. Shape C is the same length as shape B if I cut the end off and move it to the other side, but shape C is taller.</p>
  </solution>


